English: (très familier) annoying / pain in the ass
Example: ma soeur est chiante. Ce film est super chiant, ne va pas le voir.
Example Translation: My sister is annoying. This movie is super boring, don’t go and watch it.

English: (mostly legal language) with the aim of, in order to

Example: He likes to travel on his own.
Example Translation: Il aime voyager sur son propre.

French: placement de bon père de famille
Example: Il ne possédait qu’un compte épargne, un placement de bon père de famille.
Example Translation: He only had a savings account, a safe investment.

Example: I gérait son entreprise en bon père de famille.
Example Translation: He managed his company with due diligence.

Example: Il a donné à ses enfants une éducation de bon père de famille.
Example Translation: He gave his children sensible education.

Example: À l’aide ! Nous sommes coincés dans l’ascenseur.
Example Translation: Help! We are stuck in the elevator.

Example: Ce papillon est d’une grande rareté. Sa mère se plaint de la rareté de ses visites.
Example Translation: This butterfly is of great rarity. His mother complains of the scarcity of his visits.
